  • Type Parameters:
    I - 

    public class IndexedReferenceDataCache<I extends Indexed>
extends DataCache<IndexedReference<? extends I>,I>
    A DataCache keyed by IndexedReference objects. This needs no additional logic to create the target objects as the IndexedRefenece can do this directly. However the use of a cache can reduce the number of database lookups.
